```csharp

using DigitalOcean = Pulumi.DigitalOcean;

class MyStack : Stack
{
    public MyStack()
    {
        var example = Output.Create(DigitalOcean.GetDatabaseCluster.InvokeAsync(new DigitalOcean.GetDatabaseClusterArgs

            Name = "example-cluster",
        }));
        var read_only = example.Apply(example => Output.Create(DigitalOcean.GetDatabaseReplica.InvokeAsync(new DigitalOcean.GetDatabaseReplicaArgs

        })));

    }

    [Output("replicaOutput")]
    public Output<string> ReplicaOutput { get; set; }
}
```

```go
	})
```
